Package mythical.maze

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutoCloseFrame
    Closes a frame when focus is lost.
    BackgroundMusic
    Runs the music for the Mythical Maze game.
    Block
    Object class for individual game blocks.
    Character
    Creates a character object that the user can move around through the maze.
    CrashLogger
    Logs system crash to a dedicated log file.
    ErrorLogger
    Logs system errors to a dedicated log file.
    EventLogger
    Logs system event to a dedicated log file.
    GameRunner
    Class that runs the game, including starting and ending the game
    Grid
    Creates a Grid that the game will be played on; includes blocks and characters.
    HUD
    Creates a heads up display that displays user statistics, names and buttons.
    ImageManager
    Imports images for later use when called upon.
    IShape
    Object class for creating "I" shaped pieces.
    JShape
    Object class for creating "J" shaped pieces.
    LShape
    Object class for creating "L" shaped pieces.
    MainMenu
    Initiates a main menu in which the user can navigate around to find the game, log in, create new profiles, play tutorials, or find statistics.
    MiniIShape
    Object class for small "I" shapes.
    MiniJShape
    Object class for creating small "J" shapes.
    MiniLShape
    Object class for creating small "L" shapes.
    MiniOShape
    Creates a small "O" shaped piece.
    MythicalMaze
    Mythical Maze main class.
    OptionsMenu
    Pulls up a menu for user to change settings.
    OShape
    Object class that creates an "O" shape to be used in the grid
    SaveLoad
    Saves game profiles into a local file database.
    SelectPlayer
    Creates a frame in which the user can select a player slot.
    Settings
    Reads and writes game settings information to a settings file.
    Shape
    Parent class for the shape objects of the game.
    SoundFX
    Plays sound effects.
    SShape
    Object class for creating "S" shapes.
    SuperMiniIShape
    Object class for smaller "I" shapes.
    TShape
    Object class for creating "T" shaped objects.
    ZShape
    Object class for creating "Z" shapes.
